Package: planmgr
Version: 0.1.0
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: docker.io | docker-ce, curl, adduser, systemd
Maintainer: Vasiliy Zdanovskiy <vasilyvz@gmail.com>
Description: plan_manager deployment package
 Installs and configures the plan_manager server as a systemd-managed
 Docker container. Provisions the dedicated host identity and mounted
 directories, renders the server configuration from operator settings,
 verifies and pulls the required container image, and manages the
 container lifecycle through a systemd service unit.
